--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------- GEODIAG ------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:

    This is a collaborative repository, enclosing scripts (e.g., NCL) and tools
    to process and diagnose the climate model data.

    More cotents will come soon!
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Framework:

    Scripts will be organized according to phenomena in atmosphere, ocean, etc.

    Tools will contain any program code to process or prepare data for next
    diagnostics.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation:

    In BASH, add the following line in ".bashrc":

      source <path_to_geodiag>/setup.sh
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage:

    In GEODIAG, the calling of each script is through the calling of the main
    command interface as:

      $ ./geodiag

    and some questions will be asked for the necessary arguments of the script.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
